ğŸ“ Responsive Image and Button Layout (Bootstrap 4)

This layout implements a responsive hero section using **Bootstrap 4â€™s grid system** combined with minimal custom CSS to ensure consistent alignment across screen sizes.


ğŸ§± Layout Structure

The page uses a standard Bootstrap container and row:

```html
<div class="container bg">
  <div class="row">
    ...
  </div>
</div>
```

* `container` provides horizontal padding and responsive width
* `row` enables the Bootstrap grid layout
* `bg` applies a custom background color



ğŸ“± Responsive Columns

Left Column (Large screens only)

```html
<div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-sm-none d-md-none d-lg-block">
```

* Visible only on **large (lg) screens**
* Occupies half the width
* Displays the VR image as a visual element



Right Column (All screen sizes)

```html
<div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6 text-center">
```

* Full width on **small and medium** screens
* Half width on **large** screens
* Centers text and interactive elements



 ğŸ–¼ï¸ Image Rendering

```html
<img
  src="..."
  class="image img-fluid d-lg-none d-md-block"
/>
```

* `img-fluid` ensures the image scales with the container
* `d-md-block d-lg-none` controls visibility:

  * Shown on medium screens
  * Hidden on large screens
* The image stacks naturally above the button on smaller devices



ğŸ¯ Image Styling

```css
.image {
  height: 200px;
  max-width: 100%;
  display: block;
  margin: auto;
}
```

* Maintains consistent image height
* Prevents overflow on smaller screens
* Centers the image horizontally

ğŸ”˜ Call-to-Action Button

```html
<button>contact us</button>
```

```css
button {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: white;
  border: 1px solid white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  width: 130px;
  height: 30px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}


* Styled as an outlined button
* Naturally appears below the image due to block-level layout flow
* Maintains consistent spacing across breakpoints



ğŸ¨ Typography & Theme

* Google Fonts are imported for consistent typography
* The background color (`#222b36`) creates contrast
* White text and borders ensure readability



âœ… Result

* Fully responsive layout
* Image remains centered at all sizes
* Button always appears below the image
* Clean separation of layout (Bootstrap) and styling (CSS)


